## Rules

- Do not log normal implementation choices here. Only log explicit trade-offs, accepted risks, or temporary compromises.
- If a deviation affects users, trust, security, or long-term maintainability, spell that out plainly.
- Closing a deviation should include what changed and why the original compromise is no longer needed.
